name: 03- Exploratory Analysis
content:
Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)


Key Insights


Seasonal Patterns

  • Q4 Dominance: October through December account for approximately 89% of annual sales
  • Peak Period: November is the strongest month, representing 45.2% of annual sales
  • Off-Peak Period: January through September shows consistent but low business activity


Invoice Distribution

  • Peak Volume: ~250 invoices in November
  • Regular Volume: 25-35 invoices per month during January-September
  • Year-End Surge: Significant increase in invoice volume during Q4
